title: Rock & Republic Women's Denim Rx Fever Pull-On Bootcut Jean
description: BOOTCUT. This jean is both comfortable and stylish. With a flattering mid-rise, hip-hugging fabric and a leg opening that falls gracefully over your favorite boots and booties, these jeans are easy to dress up or down.

DENIM Rx SLIMMING CURE. Step into confidence with these comfortable yet stylish jeans. Using the latest advances in fiber and fit technology, Denim Rx gives you unprecedented stretch and recovery to support your curves for a slimming silhouette.
ALL-DAY COMFORT. Made from a cotton-stretch blend, these jeans provide lasting comfort, unrestricted mobility and plenty of stretch for your day ahead.
5-POCKET STYLING. Built with (3) functional pockets and (2) faux front pockets, these jeans feature classic 5-pocket styling with extra storage for your phone, keys, wallet and more.
DETAILS. Pull-on design. Inseam: Short: 32", Medium: 34", Long: 36". Rise: 10". Bottom leg opening: 17.5".
Rock & Republic Womens Denim Rx Fever Pull-On Bootcut Jean
